description: This speedy stir-fry is perfect for a no-fuss dinner. Succulent satay prawns with fluffy rice and crunchy slaw, try this fresh seafood recipe today.
name: Speedy Satay Prawn Stir-Fry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 375 g Woolworths COOK stir fry mix rainbow vegetables
1 kg Woolworths large green banana prawns
200 g Passage to Asia satay chicken stir-fry sauce
450 g Sunrice microwave jasmine fragrant white rice

recipeInstructions.text: Meanwhile, heat rice according to packet instructions. Divide rice among bowls. Top with prawn stir-fry and vegetables. Scatter over coriander and serve with lime wedges.
